**HITL stories** (need design decisions): 2 (toolbar layout), 6 (font list), 12 (numbering style UI), 17 (heading levels), 28 (encryption mechanism), 30 (cross-client QA).

**Open questions surfaced**: OQ-1 through OQ-8 from the epic are referenced in the relevant stories where they need resolution.
